description:
# Set Up Bank Accounts with Proper IBAN

Bank Accounts can be created for a Company as well as other parties like Customers, Suppliers etc. Doing this lets you record all the bank transactions correctly for accounting accuracy.

Within the bank account, you can setup a proper IBAN for that bank account.
name: Set Up Bank Accounts For Company with IBAN
title: Set Up Bank Accounts For Company with IBAN
